<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lmyn nrwḥ wạnt ạlạlh .. wʿndk wḥdk klạm ạlḥyạẗ
 lmạ bnjylk ylmsnạ rwḥk .. ysẖfy wyḥrr ạsr ạlkẖṭạẗ
 ạlqrạr- bʿywn ạlḥb tsẖwf ạldmwʿ .. fy ʿywn ạlnạs ttḥnn ʿlyhm
 wtmd ạydk tmḥy ạlạ̉nyn .. tmnḥ slạm wtṣyr rạʿyhm
 2- wʿnd ạlqbr sẖwfnạ ḥyạry̱ .. tạ̹mr fykẖrj mn ạlmwt ḥyạẗ
 wf lyl ạlḥzn tsẖrq bnwrk .. tfrḥ nfwsnạ brb ạlḥyạẗ
 3- wrgẖm ạlzḥmẗ ʿynyk btlmḥ .. qlwb ʿẓsẖạnẗ llʿysẖẗ mʿạk
 tyjy wḥḍwrk ystr mạḍynạ .. wndwq ḥlạwẗ ạlʿsẖrẗ wyạk</lyrics>
<title>bʿywn ạlḥb</title>
